'''拉娃·布拉茲·維埃拉'''（{{lang-pt|Loalwa Braz Vieira}}，{{bd|1953年|6月3日|2017年|1月19日|catIdx=Braz,Loalwa}}），[[巴西|巴西]]歌手<ref name="cespedes">{{cite journal | last1 = Céspedes | first1 = Gilka Wara | year = 1993 | title = "Huayño," "Saya," and "Chuntunqui": Bolivian Identity in the Music of "Los Kjarkas" | journal = Latin American Music Review: Revista de Música Latinoamericana | volume = 14 | pages = 52-101 | jstor = 780009}}</ref>和[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]。她最著名的作品是在法國－巴西流行樂團{{link-en|Kaoma|Kaoma}}的全球暢銷金曲《{{link-en|黏巴達 (歌曲)|Lambada (song)|黏巴達}}》中擔任主唱<ref name="cespedes"/>。她可流利地使用四種語言，除曾以[[母語|母語]][[葡萄牙文|葡萄牙文]]錄製唱片外，亦曾灌錄[[西班牙文|西班牙文]]、[[法文|法文]]和[[英文|英文]]唱片。

== 生平 ==
拉娃在[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]一個音樂家庭出生，父親是[[管絃樂團|管絃樂團]]團長，母親是[[鋼琴家|鋼琴家]]。拉娃4歲時開始學彈鋼琴，13歲開始唱歌。1985年時移居[[巴黎|巴黎]]，2010年時移居[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]直到2017年過世。

=== 遇害 ===
2017年1月19日凌晨，[[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]]警方在距里約熱內盧73公里的[[薩夸雷馬|薩夸雷馬]]一輛焚毀汽車中發現拉娃的遺體<ref name = "death">{{cite web | url = http://g1.globo.com/rj/regiao-dos-lagos/noticia/2017/01/corpo-de-loalwa-braz-do-kaoma-e-encontrado-em-carro-incendiado.html | title = Loalwa Braz, do Kaoma, é achada morta em carro incendiado, diz polícia | website = Gl.globo.com | accessdate = 2017-01-19 | archive-date = 2017-01-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170119154226/http://g1.globo.com/rj/regiao-dos-lagos/noticia/2017/01/corpo-de-loalwa-braz-do-kaoma-e-encontrado-em-carro-incendiado.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Lambada singer Loalwa Braz found dead in Brazil | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38681413 | date = 2017-01-19 | accessdate = 2017-01-19 | language = en | archive-date = 2017-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170121021438/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-38681413 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。目擊者表示曾看見兩位男子在她家附近，距前述被焚車輛被發現的地點不遠<ref name = "death"/>。拉娃名下旅館員工承認與兩名同夥犯下此案<ref>{{cite news | title = 《黏巴達》女主唱遭焚屍殺害 名下旅館23歲員工認罪 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | url = http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1954012 | date = 2017-01-20 | accessdate = 2017-01-22 | language = zh-tw | archive-date = 2017-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170121121108/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1954012 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

